info.author: Sal Uryasev
info.description:
This is an API to Google Analytics to handle authentication and automatic
download and parsing of any Google Analytics data and reports.

A detailed description can be found here:
http://www.juiceanalytics.com/openjuice/juiced-google-analytics-api/

This module is no longer supported due to the release of the gdata-based google
analytics API.
